4 immediately prior to annexation.
5 Section 7. The exemptions granted in Sections 1 and 4 of this Act and the
6 authority granted in Sections 1, 2, and 3 of this Act shall apply retroactively to January 1,
7 2020, including with regard to any activities undertaken prior to the effective date of this
8 Act by an entity to which the exemption or authority is conferred under this Act.
